# Project Structure

This is a React application built with React Router 7+, React 19+, and TailwindCSS 4+. The project follows a specific structure:

## Key Directories

- [app/](mdc:app) - Main application code. It's an app that documents the [registry/](mdc:registry)
  - [components/](mdc:app/components) - React components
    - [ui/](mdc:app/components/ui) - Reusable UI components
    - [examples/](mdc:app/components/examples) - Example implementations
  - [lib/](mdc:app/lib) - Shared utilities and helpers
  - [routes/](mdc:app/routes) - React Router route components
    - [(docs)/](mdc:app/routes/(docs)) - Documentation routes
      - [blocks/](mdc:app/routes/(docs):id/) - Documentation page for a single block component
      - [components/](mdc:app/routes/(docs):id/) - Documentation page for a single primitive component

- [registry/](mdc:registry) - Component registry
  - [basil-ui/](mdc:registry/basil-ui) - Core UI components

- [.react-router/](mdc:.react-router) - Auto-generated React Router types (do not edit)

## Configuration Files

- [react-router.config.ts](mdc:react-router.config.ts) - React Router configuration
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) - Vite bundler configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - UI components configuration


## Other

All `.local` dirs should be ignored.
